Welcome to T's Calculator

This is just a simple calculator class that uses RSpec for 
testing.  It will eventually have all the same functions as 
the calculator app on your iPhone.

Features:
  - Addition
  - Subtraction
  - Multiplication
  - Division
  - Additive Inverse
  - Exponentiation
  - Multiplicative Inverse
  - Percentage
  - Factorials
  - Roots (Square & otherwise)
  - Memory Recall
  - Memory Clear
  - Memory Add
  - Memory Subtract

Happy Calculating,
theTizzo
